org.symphonyoss.client.model

Class Room

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.symphonyoss.client.model.Room

  • public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
    Room abstraction object which identifies and holds all properties of a Symphony Room. Room objects work directly with the RoomService, which supports all room events.
